\v 2 Ndichati pamusoro paJehovha: \add Ndiye\add* utiziro hwangu\x + 91.9. Map. 94.22. Map. 14.6. Map. 9.9.\x* nenhare yangu\x + Map. 31.3. 71.3. 144.2. 2 Sam. 22.2.\x*, Mwari wangu, ndinovimba naye\x + Map. 25.2.\x*.
\v 3 Nokuti iye achakununura\x + Zvir. 6.5. Mab. 12.11.\x* kubva parudzingi rwemuteyi\x + Job. 18.9. Map. 69.22. 119.110. 124.7. 140.5. 141.9. 142.3. Hos. 5.1. 9.8. Map. 11.6.\x*, kubva pahosha yekuparadza kukuru\x + Map. 52.2.\x*.
\v 4 Achakufukidza neminhenga yake\x + Job. 39.13.\x*, uye uchavimba pasi pemapapiro ake\x + Map. 17.8. Map. 121.5.\x*\x + Job. 39.13.\x*\x + Rut. 2.12. Mat. 23.37. Ruk. 13.34.\x*; chokwadi chake inhovo huru nenhovo diki\x + Map. 35.2.\x*.
\v 5 Haungatyi chinotyisa pausiku, museve unobhururuka masikati\x + Job. 5.19,23. Zvir. 3.23-26. Isa. 43.2.\x*,
\v 6 hosha inofamba murima\x + Job. 10.22.\x*, kuparadza kunoputsa masikati machena\x + Det. 32.24. Isa. 28.2. Hos. 13.14.\x*.
\v 7 Kurutivi rwako kuchawa churu, negumi rezvuru paruoko rwako rwerudyi; hazvingaswederi kwauri.
