\v 8 Koga unotarisa nemeso ako; ndokuona kutsiviwa kwevakaipa\x + Map. 37.34. Mara. 1.5.\x*.
\v 9 Nokuti imwi Jehovha muri utiziro hwangu\x + 91.9. Map. 94.22. Map. 14.6. Map. 9.9.\x*! Wakaita Wekumusoro-soro ave nzvimbo yako yekugara\x + Det. 33.27.\x*.
\v 10 Hapana chakaipa chingakuwira\x + Zvir. 12.21. Job. 5.19.\x*, uye dambudziko ripi neripi haringaswederi\x + Map. 38.11.\x* patende rako\x + Job. 8.22.\x*.
\v 11 Nokuti acharaira\x + Mat. 4.6. Ruk. 4.10,11.\x* vatumwa vake pamusoro pako, kukuchengetedza panzira dzako dzose\x + Map. 34.7. Mat. 18.10.\x*.
\v 12 Vachakusimudza pamaoko, zvimwe urovere rutsoka rwako pabwe\x + Zvir. 3.23. Map. 37.24.\x*.
\v 13 Uchatsika\x + Ruk. 10.19.\x* pamusoro peshumba nechiva\x + Job. 10.16.\x*; mwana weshumba nebukanana uchatsikirira pasi\x + Map. 74.13.\x*.
